<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbf5a4c9d-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s11925"><num value="11925">§ 11925.</num><heading> Regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Not later than 6 months after <date date="1988-11-18">November 18, 1988</date>, the Secretary shall issue any regulations necessary to carry out this subchapter.</p>
